_affiliate.png?9d7bd4\" alt=\"Friendship is a great thing - join our affiliate program\" width=\"285\" height=\"180\" />A quick update for all our affiliates: we&#8217;ve just added the <a href=\"http://developers.slidedeck.com\" target=\"_blank\">SlideDeck.js Developers&#8217; Kit</a> to our affiliate program! Now, you can earn even more commissions by referring visitors, which is specially designed to enable Web developers to create beautiful, custom jQuery sliders in minutes.</p>\n<p>Even better: <strong>all the standard terms apply, meaning you&#8217;ll still earn between $12 to $50 per sale!</strong></p>\n<p>All you need to do is <a href=\"http://member.impactradius.com/advertiser-applycampaign-info/digital-telepathy.brand?c=1130\" target=\"_blank\">log into your Impact Radius account</a>, grab the appropriate ads or links, and place them on your site, to start driving traffic.</p>\n<h3>Not an affiliate yet?</h3>\n<p>Now&#8217;s a great time to consider joining &#8211; it&#8217;s free, takes less than 10 minutes to set up and you can <strong>earn at least 25% commission per sale.</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://member.impactradius.com/advertiser-applycampaign-info/digital-telepathy.brand?c=1130\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-10378\" title=\"Sign up for the SlideDeck 2 Affiliate Program\" src=\"http://assets-slidedeck2.s3.amazonaws.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/IR_signup_CTA_button.png?9d7bd4\" alt=\"Sign up for the SlideDeck 2 Affiliate Program\" width=\"306\" height=\"66\" /></a></p>\n<br/><br/><a href=\"http://www.slidedeck.com/pricing/?utm_source=feed_ad&utm_medium=banner&utm_campaign=sd_blog\"><img src=\"//s3.amazonaws.com/assets-slidedeck2/wp-content/themes/slidedeck2/images/sd-rss.jpg?9d7bd4\" alt=\"Easily create AWESOME WordPress sliders - Get SlideDeck\" style=\"display:block;border:none;\"/></a><div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/Slidedeck?a=GANLNW9wtNc:Aa9iZNfYdn4:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds