hoose a 100% GPL theme license. However, as a customer, its difficult to find where those 100% GPL licensed themes are located on the site. Upon browsing the Themeforest Marketplace, I could not find a category, tag, or link that would show me all the WordPress themes licensed as such. [&hellip;]\'>WPTavern: How To Search For 100% GPL Themes On Themeforest</a></li><li><a class=\'rsswidget\' href=\'http://wordpress.tv/2013/05/07/john-p-bloch-awesome-helper-functions-in-wordpress-core/\' title=\' [&hellip;]\'>WordPress.tv: John P. Bloch: Awesome Helper Functions in WordPress Core</a></li><li><a class=\'rsswidget\' href=\'http://wordpress.tv/2013/05/07/brad-parbs-320px-and-up-getting-started-with-responsive-design-2/\' title=\' [&hellip;]\'>WordPress.tv: Brad Parbs: 320px and Up, Getting Started with Responsive Design</a></li><li><a class=\'rsswidget\' href=\'http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/WordpressTavern/~3/-9bfGAH0eWA/pressnomics-conference-announces-date-for-2013\' title=\'The folks behind Pressnomics have announced the dates for this years conference. It will be held on October 17th-19th. For those that dont know, Pressnomics is a conference centered around the services and products that have created a successful and diverse economy around WordPress. Tickets go on sale June 19th at 10am PST and will be released in batches. F [&hellip;]\'>WPTavern: Pressnomics Conference Announces Date For 2013</a></li><li><a class=\'rsswidget\' href=\'http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/WordpressTavern/~3/19hutSdYz4I/searching-for-a-better-wordpress-search\' title=\'On May 6th, the WordPress VIP team blog announced a new VIP service theyll be offering centered around search. While at first it may be surprising that the default search in WordPress was not used in their latest project, the fact is, WordPress search in its current state can not perform complex search queries without using a considerable amount of computat [&hellip;]\'>WPTavern: Searching For A Better WordPress Search</a></